----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
OPENAI CHATGPT ADS PIXEL (installed 2026-05-15)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Init script for ChatGPT Ads conversion tracking. Pixel ID: REPLACE_WITH_BOUNTY_OPENAI_PIXEL
Account: thebountybasket.com data source in OpenAI Ads Manager (Go-To Gifting LLC).

NOTE: debug:true is currently ON — flip to false (or remove the line) once we confirm events are firing
correctly in the OpenAI Ads Manager.

Conversion events (oaiq("measure", ...)) are intentionally NOT installed globally here — they must fire
only on the specific action being tracked (purchase on order confirmation, registration on account
creation, etc.) or they will fire on every page load and pollute the data.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
{%- endcomment -%}
<script>
  !function(w, d, s, u) {
    if (w.oaiq) return;
    var q = function() {
      q.q.push(arguments);
    };
    q.q = [];
    w.oaiq = q;
    var j = d.createElement(s);
    j.async = 1;
    j.src = u;
    var f = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];
    f.parentNode.insertBefore(j, f);
  }(window, document, "script", "https://bzrcdn.openai.com/sdk/oaiq.min.js");
  oaiq("init", {
    pixelId: "REPLACE_WITH_BOUNTY_OPENAI_PIXEL",
    debug: true
  });
</script>
<!-- End OpenAI ChatGPT Ads Pixel -->

